comments: Sabonis (SAC) is leaning toward Booker's (PHX) path and marginal body contact occurs as the two briefly come together.
Fox (SAC) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Gordon (PHX) and is not in a legal guarding position as contact occurs with Gordon.
Beal (PHX) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn

comments: Sabonis (SAC) is moving laterally toward Booker's (PHX) path and marginal body contact occurs as the two come together during Booker's drive.

Sabonis (SAC) firms up in a screening position in Allen's (PHX) path.  When Allen commits to going underneath the pick, marginal contact occurs as the two players move in the same direction.  Sabonis then inadvertently trips over Allen's foot as the two players disengage.

Sabonis (SAC) brings his arm across Booker's (PHX) front and as Booker lifts his own arm to disengage, Sabonis loses his balance.  Sabonis initiates the contact between the two players, but the contact is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) extends an arm toward Durant's (PHX) back and affects his ability to pursue the loose ball.

Gordon (PHX) is late to the spot when marginal body contact occurs with Fox (SAC) as the two come together during the driving shot attempt.  Fox does not extend his arm into Gordon to dislodge him from his defensive position.
Fox (SAC) makes contact with Durant's (PHX) right arm, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Beal (PHX) briefly has a hand placed at Fox's (SAC) side during the throw-in, but Fox stumbles and loses his balance on his own.
Gordon (PHX) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Monk's (SAC) arms.
